resolution: Handled the linked-test sandbox ENOENT race by ignoring ENOENT during optional seed copy after existence preflight.
expected_result: Stale or concurrently removed sandbox seed paths should not create handled Sentry errors or fail linked-test execution.
actual_result: "pnpm build, focused linked-test tests, pm linked-test run, and full coverage passed; Sentry PM-CLI-P root cause documented."
