  "2026-05-11T22:30:40.812Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: fixed Sentry PM-CLI-P by treating ENOENT during linked-test sandbox seed copy as a benign missing-source race after the preflight; pnpm build passed; PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts passed (34 tests); pm test pm-kk4t --run --progress passed; full coverage passed at 100% statements/branches/functions/lines across 91 files and 1284 tests."
